    * Fixed unregistered bug
        Crash occured in service gfix code when it tried to reattach to currently 
        unavailable database. Since service can't interact with end user an endless 
        loop leads to overflow service buffer and crash as result.
      Contributor(s):
        Vlad Horsun <horsun at kdb.dp.ua>

